docs.lead_paragraph: While ploughing her way through the darkness of the early morning the North German Lloyd liner Kronprinz Wilhelm on Monday collided with an iceberg off the Banks, and but for quick work on her bridge and equally quick response in her engine room she would have crept into port badly crippled, if she ever got in at all.
docs.abstract: North German Lloyd liner Kronprinz Wilhelm collides with iceberg; arrives in Hoboken with only slight damage

headline.main: GIANT KRONPRINZ HITS AN ICEBERG; Only Quick Action Prevents a Disaster at Night Off the Banks. SCRAPE SIDES, DENT BOW Big Liner Gets Within 100 Feet of the Berg Before It Is Seen -- Tons of Ice Fall on Deck.

docs.lead_paragraph: THE HAGUE, July 17. -- The British proposal for the limitation of armaments requests that the Peace Conference confirm the resolution on the subject adopted by the first Peace Conference, and, as the question has become more urgent, it exhorts the Governments represented at the second conference to give it careful study.

docs.lead_paragraph: I is difficult to prophesy, with any certainty, future prospects in the flour trade at the present time owing to the delayed marketing of the Winter wheat crop, which is from two to three weeks behind the seasonal average. However, there is nothing to indicate a material change in conditions, and it is likely that the estimate of the Winter wheat crop of between 395,000,000 and 400,000,000 bushels is near right.

headline.main: WHEAT SITUATION STRONG.; American Flour Journal's Editor Says It Means Continued Prosperity.

docs.snippet: THE HAGUE, Aug. 3. -- Another American proposition -- the establishment of a permanent Court of Arbitration at The Hague -- to-day obtained a splendid success in the sub-committee which had the matter in hand. Twenty-seven delegates voted for it and...
docs.lead_paragraph: THE HAGUE, Aug. 3. -- Another American proposition -- the establishment of a permanent Court of Arbitration at The Hague -- to-day obtained a splendid success in the sub-committee which had the matter in hand. Twenty-seven delegates voted for it and twelve abstained from voting. This means that the proposal was unanimously approved.

headline.main: FOR A PERMANENT COURT.; Peace Conference Committee Unanimously Approves Our Plan.
